  <footer>
    <p>Made with ❤️ for a beginner's HTML journey &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span>Keep building!</span></p>
    <p style="margin-top:6px">Next step → learn <strong>CSS</strong> to make it beautiful, then <strong>JavaScript</strong> to make it interactive.</p>
  </footer>

</div>
